  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >\"Select the shape, drag & drop to the map\"</h2><br>Your objective of this game is to connect a conductor line of the same color to a \"●\"<br><br><br><br><strong>Main features</strong><br>・Over 18 stages! Reasonable volume.<br><br>・Contains original music! You can play it on a loop forever during gameplay.<br><br>・Cheap price! You would have a chance to buy with the remaining credit if you bought a full-price game.<br><br><br><strong>Sub features</strong><br><br><strong>◆ Color-changing gimmick</strong><br>   Use the rectangular block to change the color of electricity. Color flows from blue --> red<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045540/extras/bd5463d7f85dbaf0867edbef88732fa7.poster.avif?t=1729696827\" width=400 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045540/extras/bd5463d7f85dbaf0867edbef88732fa7.webm?t=1729696827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045540/extras/bd5463d7f85dbaf0867edbef88732fa7.mp4?t=1729696827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>◆Expand map</strong><br>   This game does not have a limitation of map length. The circuit board can be expanded by placing shapes on the outer edges of it.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045540/extras/ae4213f5de069e3ea38a2eb5da0ce1f1.poster.avif?t=1729696827\" width=400 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045540/extras/ae4213f5de069e3ea38a2eb5da0ce1f1.webm?t=1729696827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045540/extras/ae4213f5de069e3ea38a2eb5da0ce1f1.mp4?t=1729696827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>◆Direction block</strong><br>   It can change the way you draw the conductor line, but in most situation they don't go where you want to be.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045540/extras/0f73ee3a968f93e77b266a804ccb252f.poster.avif?t=1729696827\" width=400 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045540/extras/0f73ee3a968f93e77b266a804ccb252f.webm?t=1729696827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045540/extras/0f73ee3a968f93e77b266a804ccb252f.mp4?t=1729696827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>When a stage is too difficult, you can skip the whole stage by pressing the <strong>S key</strong>!<br><br>Thanks for your interest.",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >\"Select the shape, drag & drop to the map\"</h2><br>Your objective of this game is to connect a conductor line of the same color to a \"●\"<br><br><br><br><strong>Main features</strong><br>・Over 18 stages! Reasonable volume.<br><br>・Contains original music! You can play it on a loop forever during gameplay.<br><br>・Cheap price! You would have a chance to buy with the remaining credit if you bought a full-price game.<br><br><br><strong>Sub features</strong><br><br><strong>◆ Color-changing gimmick</strong><br>   Use the rectangular block to change the color of electricity. Color flows from blue --> red<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045540/extras/bd5463d7f85dbaf0867edbef88732fa7.poster.avif?t=1729696827\" width=400 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045540/extras/bd5463d7f85dbaf0867edbef88732fa7.webm?t=1729696827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045540/extras/bd5463d7f85dbaf0867edbef88732fa7.mp4?t=1729696827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>◆Expand map</strong><br>   This game does not have a limitation of map length. The circuit board can be expanded by placing shapes on the outer edges of it.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045540/extras/ae4213f5de069e3ea38a2eb5da0ce1f1.poster.avif?t=1729696827\" width=400 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045540/extras/ae4213f5de069e3ea38a2eb5da0ce1f1.webm?t=1729696827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045540/extras/ae4213f5de069e3ea38a2eb5da0ce1f1.mp4?t=1729696827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>◆Direction block</strong><br>   It can change the way you draw the conductor line, but in most situation they don't go where you want to be.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045540/extras/0f73ee3a968f93e77b266a804ccb252f.poster.avif?t=1729696827\" width=400 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045540/extras/0f73ee3a968f93e77b266a804ccb252f.webm?t=1729696827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045540/extras/0f73ee3a968f93e77b266a804ccb252f.mp4?t=1729696827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>When a stage is too difficult, you can skip the whole stage by pressing the <strong>S key</strong>!<br><br>Thanks for your interest.",
